msgstr "ascii;konvertera;konvertering;text;ansi;"

#: data/dev.geopjr.Calligraphy.metainfo.xml.in:12
msgid ""
"Calligraphy turns short texts into large, impressive banners made up of "
"ASCII Characters, ready to be copied or exported to images. Spice up your "
"online conversations by adding some extra oompf to your messages!"
msgstr ""
"Calligraphy förvandlar korta texter till stora, imponerande banderoller "
"bestående av ASCII-tecken, redo att kopieras eller exporteras till bilder. "
"Krydda upp dina onlinekonversationer genom att lägga till lite extra kraft i "
"dina meddelanden!"

